      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 50,
      "message": "Does extending the MsoGroovyTest provide any benefits in case of this test class? If not I'd recommend removing it and avoid using inheritance in the future in such cases since unmaintained the implementation often stiffens the design and can cause a ripple effect during changes.",
      "author": {
